  "description": [
    "THE NOME NUGGET Published Monday Wednesday and Friday by the NOME PUBLISHING GO NOME ALASKA Telephone Main 125 150 PER MONTH PO Box 618 1600 A YEAR E P BOUCHER Managing Editor CLINTON GRAY Production Manager Entered as second class matter October 14 1943 at the post office at Nome Alaska under Act of March 3 1879 Subscribers hot receiving their paper by 530 pm call Main 125 for special delivery After 530 call Black 102 WELL YQU CANT PLEASE EVERYBODY mm Success Usually Begins With Saving And Saving Begins With a Plan at the MINERS MERCHANTS BANK OF ALASKA NOME ALASKA WE WILL BUILD NOME WITH YOU BACK TO SCHOOL Skirts Slacks Jackets Sweaters SEEN IN CHARM AND GLAMOUR DOROTHYS SHOP Nome Shriners Get Charter Monday evening Shriners and 32d Degree Masons and their la dies were guests of Nile Temple at a dinner at the Seaview Dining Room at which time the charter for the Nome Shrine Club was presented An outstanding local Mason Norvin Lewis Fast Master and Secretary of the local Anvil Lodge for many years nd the only local 33rd Degree Mason was among the few missing eli bles to the party as he is"
